Ms. Nguyễn Thị Bích, born in 1966 (Member # 010102140032). She lives with her husband and 2 children. She does farming and has a small general store. Her husband assists her with the store and purchasing merchandise. One son is a laborer, and the other son is getting his higher education. Her family's income per month is 230 USD. She is very enthusiastic and outgoing; therefore, the group selected her to be the leader. Her group consists of: 

Ms. Cao Thị Lưu, born in 1966 (Member # 010102140012). She does farming and has a small general store. She joined the fund to borrow 265 USD to buy and sell meat;
Ms .Trần Thị Lương, born in 1971 (Member # 010102140033). She joined the fund to borrow 265 USD to sell breakfast food and raising animals;
Ms. Nguyễn Thị Hà, born in 1971 (Member # 010102140035). She joined the fund to borrow 240 USD to sell chicken meat;
Ms. Lại Thị Bẩy, born in 1959 (Member # 010102140034). She joined the fund to borrow 265 USD to raise pigs




